{"segment_id": "mozi-004-methods-and-standards__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0001", "section_id": "mozi-004-methods-and-standards", "source_id": "mozi-004-methods-and-standards__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 1, "text_original": "子墨子曰：", "text_normalized": "子墨子曰：", "canonical_ref": "4.1", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-004-methods-and-standards__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0002", "section_id": "mozi-004-methods-and-standards", "source_id": "mozi-004-methods-and-standards__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 2, "text_original": "天下從事者，不可以無法儀。", "text_normalized": "天下從事者，不可以無法儀。", "canonical_ref": "4.2", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-004-methods-and-standards__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0003", "section_id": "mozi-004-methods-and-standards", "source_id": "mozi-004-methods-and-standards__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 3, "text_original": "無法儀而其事能成者，無有也。", "text_normalized": "無法儀而其事能成者，無有也。", "canonical_ref": "4.3", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-004-methods-and-standards__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0004", "section_id": "mozi-004-methods-and-standards", "source_id": "mozi-004-methods-and-standards__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 4, "text_original": "雖至士之爲將相者皆有法，雖至百工從事者亦皆有法。", "text_normalized": "雖至士之爲將相者皆有法，雖至百工從事者亦皆有法。", "canonical_ref": "4.4", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-004-methods-and-standards__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0005", "section_id": "mozi-004-methods-and-standards", "source_id": "mozi-004-methods-and-standards__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 5, "text_original": "百工爲方以矩，爲圓以規，直以繩，正以縣。", "text_normalized": "百工爲方以矩，爲圓以規，直以繩，正以縣。", "canonical_ref": "4.5", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-004-methods-and-standards__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0006", "section_id": "mozi-004-methods-and-standards", "source_id": "mozi-004-methods-and-standards__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 6, "text_original": "無巧工不巧工，皆以此五者爲法。", "text_normalized": "無巧工不巧工，皆以此五者爲法。", "canonical_ref": "4.6", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-004-methods-and-standards__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0007", "section_id": "mozi-004-methods-and-standards", "source_id": "mozi-004-methods-and-standards__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 7, "text_original": "巧者能中之，不巧者雖不能中，放依以從事，猶逾己。", "text_normalized": "巧者能中之，不巧者雖不能中，放依以從事，猶逾己。", "canonical_ref": "4.7", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-004-methods-and-standards__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0008", "section_id": "mozi-004-methods-and-standards", "source_id": "mozi-004-methods-and-standards__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 8, "text_original": "故百工從事，皆有法所度。", "text_normalized": "故百工從事，皆有法所度。", "canonical_ref": "4.8", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-004-methods-and-standards__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0009", "section_id": "mozi-004-methods-and-standards", "source_id": "mozi-004-methods-and-standards__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 9, "text_original": "今大者治天下，其次治大國，而無法所度，此不若百工辯也。", "text_normalized": "今大者治天下，其次治大國，而無法所度，此不若百工辯也。", "canonical_ref": "4.9", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-004-methods-and-standards__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0010", "section_id": "mozi-004-methods-and-standards", "source_id": "mozi-004-methods-and-standards__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 10, "text_original": "然則奚以爲治法而可？", "text_normalized": "然則奚以爲治法而可？", "canonical_ref": "4.10", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-004-methods-and-standards__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0011", "section_id": "mozi-004-methods-and-standards", "source_id": "mozi-004-methods-and-standards__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 11, "text_original": "當皆法其父母奚若？", "text_normalized": "當皆法其父母奚若？", "canonical_ref": "4.11", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-004-methods-and-standards__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0012", "section_id": "mozi-004-methods-and-standards", "source_id": "mozi-004-methods-and-standards__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 12, "text_original": "天下之爲父母者衆，而仁者寡，若皆法其父母，此法不仁也。", "text_normalized": "天下之爲父母者衆，而仁者寡，若皆法其父母，此法不仁也。", "canonical_ref": "4.12", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-004-methods-and-standards__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0013", "section_id": "mozi-004-methods-and-standards", "source_id": "mozi-004-methods-and-standards__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 13, "text_original": "法不仁，不可以爲法。", "text_normalized": "法不仁，不可以爲法。", "canonical_ref": "4.13", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-004-methods-and-standards__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0014", "section_id": "mozi-004-methods-and-standards", "source_id": "mozi-004-methods-and-standards__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 14, "text_original": "當皆法其學奚若？", "text_normalized": "當皆法其學奚若？", "canonical_ref": "4.14", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-004-methods-and-standards__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0015", "section_id": "mozi-004-methods-and-standards", "source_id": "mozi-004-methods-and-standards__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 15, "text_original": "天下之爲學者眾，而仁者寡，若皆法其學，此法不仁也。", "text_normalized": "天下之爲學者眾，而仁者寡，若皆法其學，此法不仁也。", "canonical_ref": "4.15", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-004-methods-and-standards__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0016", "section_id": "mozi-004-methods-and-standards", "source_id": "mozi-004-methods-and-standards__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 16, "text_original": "法不仁，不可以爲法。", "text_normalized": "法不仁，不可以爲法。", "canonical_ref": "4.16", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-004-methods-and-standards__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0017", "section_id": "mozi-004-methods-and-standards", "source_id": "mozi-004-methods-and-standards__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 17, "text_original": "當皆法其君奚若？", "text_normalized": "當皆法其君奚若？", "canonical_ref": "4.17", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-004-methods-and-standards__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0018", "section_id": "mozi-004-methods-and-standards", "source_id": "mozi-004-methods-and-standards__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 18, "text_original": "天下之爲君者眾，而仁者寡，若皆法其君，此法不仁也。", "text_normalized": "天下之爲君者眾，而仁者寡，若皆法其君，此法不仁也。", "canonical_ref": "4.18", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-004-methods-and-standards__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0019", "section_id": "mozi-004-methods-and-standards", "source_id": "mozi-004-methods-and-standards__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 19, "text_original": "法不仁，不可以爲法。", "text_normalized": "法不仁，不可以爲法。", "canonical_ref": "4.19", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-004-methods-and-standards__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0020", "section_id": "mozi-004-methods-and-standards", "source_id": "mozi-004-methods-and-standards__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 20, "text_original": "故父母、學、君三者，莫可以爲治法。", "text_normalized": "故父母、學、君三者，莫可以爲治法。", "canonical_ref": "4.20", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-004-methods-and-standards__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0021", "section_id": "mozi-004-methods-and-standards", "source_id": "mozi-004-methods-and-standards__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 21, "text_original": "然則奚以爲治法而可？", "text_normalized": "然則奚以爲治法而可？", "canonical_ref": "4.21", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-004-methods-and-standards__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0022", "section_id": "mozi-004-methods-and-standards", "source_id": "mozi-004-methods-and-standards__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 22, "text_original": "故曰：", "text_normalized": "故曰：", "canonical_ref": "4.22", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-004-methods-and-standards__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0023", "section_id": "mozi-004-methods-and-standards", "source_id": "mozi-004-methods-and-standards__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 23, "text_original": "莫若法天。", "text_normalized": "莫若法天。", "canonical_ref": "4.23", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-004-methods-and-standards__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0024", "section_id": "mozi-004-methods-and-standards", "source_id": "mozi-004-methods-and-standards__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 24, "text_original": "天之行廣而無私，其施厚而不德，其明久而不衰，故聖王法之。", "text_normalized": "天之行廣而無私，其施厚而不德，其明久而不衰，故聖王法之。", "canonical_ref": "4.24", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-004-methods-and-standards__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0025", "section_id": "mozi-004-methods-and-standards", "source_id": "mozi-004-methods-and-standards__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 25, "text_original": "旣以天爲法，動作有爲必度於天，天之所欲則爲之，天所不欲則止。", "text_normalized": "旣以天爲法，動作有爲必度於天，天之所欲則爲之，天所不欲則止。", "canonical_ref": "4.25", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-004-methods-and-standards__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0026", "section_id": "mozi-004-methods-and-standards", "source_id": "mozi-004-methods-and-standards__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 26, "text_original": "然而天何欲何惡者也？", "text_normalized": "然而天何欲何惡者也？", "canonical_ref": "4.26", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-004-methods-and-standards__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0027", "section_id": "mozi-004-methods-and-standards", "source_id": "mozi-004-methods-and-standards__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 27, "text_original": "天必欲人之相愛相利，而不欲人之相惡相賊也。", "text_normalized": "天必欲人之相愛相利，而不欲人之相惡相賊也。", "canonical_ref": "4.27", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-004-methods-and-standards__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0028", "section_id": "mozi-004-methods-and-standards", "source_id": "mozi-004-methods-and-standards__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 28, "text_original": "奚以知天之欲人之相愛相利，而不欲人之相惡相賊也？", "text_normalized": "奚以知天之欲人之相愛相利，而不欲人之相惡相賊也？", "canonical_ref": "4.28", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-004-methods-and-standards__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0029", "section_id": "mozi-004-methods-and-standards", "source_id": "mozi-004-methods-and-standards__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 29, "text_original": "以其兼而愛之、兼而利之也。", "text_normalized": "以其兼而愛之、兼而利之也。", "canonical_ref": "4.29", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-004-methods-and-standards__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0030", "section_id": "mozi-004-methods-and-standards", "source_id": "mozi-004-methods-and-standards__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 30, "text_original": "奚以知天兼而愛之、兼而利之也？", "text_normalized": "奚以知天兼而愛之、兼而利之也？", "canonical_ref": "4.30", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-004-methods-and-standards__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0031", "section_id": "mozi-004-methods-and-standards", "source_id": "mozi-004-methods-and-standards__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 31, "text_original": "以其兼而有之、兼而食之也。", "text_normalized": "以其兼而有之、兼而食之也。", "canonical_ref": "4.31", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-004-methods-and-standards__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0032", "section_id": "mozi-004-methods-and-standards", "source_id": "mozi-004-methods-and-standards__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 32, "text_original": "今天下無小大國，皆天之邑也。", "text_normalized": "今天下無小大國，皆天之邑也。", "canonical_ref": "4.32", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-004-methods-and-standards__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0033", "section_id": "mozi-004-methods-and-standards", "source_id": "mozi-004-methods-and-standards__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 33, "text_original": "人無幼長貴賤，皆天之臣也。", "text_normalized": "人無幼長貴賤，皆天之臣也。", "canonical_ref": "4.33", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-004-methods-and-standards__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0034", "section_id": "mozi-004-methods-and-standards", "source_id": "mozi-004-methods-and-standards__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 34, "text_original": "此以莫不犓羊，豢犬豬，絜爲酒醴粢盛，以敬事天。", "text_normalized": "此以莫不犓羊，豢犬豬，絜爲酒醴粢盛，以敬事天。", "canonical_ref": "4.34", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-004-methods-and-standards__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0035", "section_id": "mozi-004-methods-and-standards", "source_id": "mozi-004-methods-and-standards__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 35, "text_original": "此不爲兼而有之、兼而食之邪？", "text_normalized": "此不爲兼而有之、兼而食之邪？", "canonical_ref": "4.35", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-004-methods-and-standards__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0036", "section_id": "mozi-004-methods-and-standards", "source_id": "mozi-004-methods-and-standards__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 36, "text_original": "天苟兼而有食之，夫奚說以不欲人之相愛相利也？", "text_normalized": "天苟兼而有食之，夫奚說以不欲人之相愛相利也？", "canonical_ref": "4.36", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-004-methods-and-standards__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0037", "section_id": "mozi-004-methods-and-standards", "source_id": "mozi-004-methods-and-standards__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 37, "text_original": "故曰：", "text_normalized": "故曰：", "canonical_ref": "4.37", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-004-methods-and-standards__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0038", "section_id": "mozi-004-methods-and-standards", "source_id": "mozi-004-methods-and-standards__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 38, "text_original": "「愛人利人者，天必福之。", "text_normalized": "「愛人利人者，天必福之。", "canonical_ref": "4.38", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-004-methods-and-standards__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0039", "section_id": "mozi-004-methods-and-standards", "source_id": "mozi-004-methods-and-standards__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 39, "text_original": "惡人賊人者，天必禍之。", "text_normalized": "惡人賊人者，天必禍之。", "canonical_ref": "4.39", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-004-methods-and-standards__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0040", "section_id": "mozi-004-methods-and-standards", "source_id": "mozi-004-methods-and-standards__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 40, "text_original": "日殺不辜者，得不祥焉。", "text_normalized": "日殺不辜者，得不祥焉。", "canonical_ref": "4.40", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-004-methods-and-standards__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0041", "section_id": "mozi-004-methods-and-standards", "source_id": "mozi-004-methods-and-standards__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 41, "text_original": "」夫奚說人爲其相殺而天與禍乎？", "text_normalized": "」夫奚說人爲其相殺而天與禍乎？", "canonical_ref": "4.41", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-004-methods-and-standards__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0042", "section_id": "mozi-004-methods-and-standards", "source_id": "mozi-004-methods-and-standards__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 42, "text_original": "是以知天欲人相愛相利，而不欲人相惡相賊也。", "text_normalized": "是以知天欲人相愛相利，而不欲人相惡相賊也。", "canonical_ref": "4.42", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-004-methods-and-standards__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0043", "section_id": "mozi-004-methods-and-standards", "source_id": "mozi-004-methods-and-standards__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 43, "text_original": "昔之聖王禹、湯、文、武，兼愛天下之百姓，率以尊天事鬼，其利人多，故天福之，使立爲天子，天下諸侯皆賓事之。", "text_normalized": "昔之聖王禹、湯、文、武，兼愛天下之百姓，率以尊天事鬼，其利人多，故天福之，使立爲天子，天下諸侯皆賓事之。", "canonical_ref": "4.43", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-004-methods-and-standards__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0044", "section_id": "mozi-004-methods-and-standards", "source_id": "mozi-004-methods-and-standards__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 44, "text_original": "暴王桀、紂、幽、厲，兼惡天下之百姓，率以詬天侮鬼，其賊人多，故天禍之，使遂失其國家，身死爲僇於天下，後世子孫毀之，至今不息。", "text_normalized": "暴王桀、紂、幽、厲，兼惡天下之百姓，率以詬天侮鬼，其賊人多，故天禍之，使遂失其國家，身死爲僇於天下，後世子孫毀之，至今不息。", "canonical_ref": "4.44", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-004-methods-and-standards__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0045", "section_id": "mozi-004-methods-and-standards", "source_id": "mozi-004-methods-and-standards__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 45, "text_original": "故爲不善以得禍者，桀、紂、幽、厲是也；", "text_normalized": "故爲不善以得禍者，桀、紂、幽、厲是也；", "canonical_ref": "4.45", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-004-methods-and-standards__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0046", "section_id": "mozi-004-methods-and-standards", "source_id": "mozi-004-methods-and-standards__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 46, "text_original": "愛人利人以得福者，禹、湯、文、武是也。", "text_normalized": "愛人利人以得福者，禹、湯、文、武是也。", "canonical_ref": "4.46", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-004-methods-and-standards__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0047", "section_id": "mozi-004-methods-and-standards", "source_id": "mozi-004-methods-and-standards__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 47, "text_original": "愛人利人以得福者有矣，惡人賊人以得禍者亦有矣。", "text_normalized": "愛人利人以得福者有矣，惡人賊人以得禍者亦有矣。", "canonical_ref": "4.47", "notes": ""}
